    <text>
        <body>
            <div style="handwritten" type="letter" xml:id="d.1">
                <head type="title">Cornelis De Schrijver to Miklós Oláh (Antwerp, 24 September
                    1536)</head>
                <floatingText>
                    <body>
                        <p xml:id="reg.p.1">He is sending the piece he has written for the Queen,
                            which his brother has printed, along with other works he has published.
                            He placed an epigram on the cover so the whole world knows how good Oláh
                            has been to him. He is also sending the epigrams he wrote on Erasmus of
                            Rotterdam’s death. He is recommending him to Cornelis de Schepper and
                            Maximiliaan van Zevenbergen.</p>
                    </body>
                </floatingText>
                <pb/>
                <p xml:id="p.1">Cornelius Grapheus Nicolao Olao salutem. </p>
                <p xml:id="p.2">Magnifice Domine! Quem dicavi augustissimae
                        <persName>reginae</persName> libellum,<note type="critic" xml:id="note.1"
                            ><hi rend="italic">Ad optimam heroidem Mariam, Hungariae reginam,
                            sacrorum bucolicorum aeglogae tres</hi>, see Ep.
                            551.<ref>olahus.tei.15351201_1</ref></note> eum una cum aliis nonnullis
                    per <persName>fratrem</persName><note type="critic" xml:id="note.2">Johannes
                        Grapheus was a printer in Antwerp.</note> meum excusum, <milestone unit="pb"
                    />tandem ad te mitto. Ut autem mundus non ignoret tuum erga me beneficium, nempe
                    te mihi exhibendo libello apud reginam fuisse ducem, posui pro fronte libelli
                    epigramma, quo mea Musa meam erga te testatur gratitudinem. Epitaphia quoque,
                    quae <persName>Erasmo</persName> demortuo scripsi, ad te cum praesentibus misi.
                    Te vero oro, ut haec qualia, qualia sunt, boni consulas. Vale et me amicis
                    commenda, praesertim domino <persName>Cornelio Sceppero</persName><note
                        type="critic" xml:id="note.3">Cornelis de Schepper.</note> et
                        <persName>Maximiliano Transilvano</persName>,<note type="critic"
                        xml:id="note.4">Maximiliaan van Zevenbergen.</note> ad quem quoque privatim
                    scribo. Rursum vale. </p>
                <p xml:id="p.3"><placeName>Antverpiae</placeName> VIII. Kalendas Octobris anno
                    MDXXXVI. </p>
                <p xml:id="p.4"
                    ><?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?>[Epitaphium
                    domini Erasmi Roterodami per Grapheum]<?oxy_custom_end?><note type="critic"
                        xml:id="note.5"><hi rend="smallcap">Ipolyi</hi> 1875, 586–587. In Romanian:
                            <hi rend="smallcap">Albu–Capoianu</hi> 1974, 157–158; <hi
                            rend="smallcap">Capoianu–Costa–Nicolae</hi> 2022,
                    1402–1405.</note><?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?></p>
                <p xml:id="p.5">[Aliud]<?oxy_custom_end?><note type="critic" xml:id="note.6"><hi
                            rend="smallcap">Ipolyi</hi> 1875, 587. In Romanian: <hi rend="smallcap"
                            >Albu–Capoianu</hi> 1974, 158; <hi rend="smallcap"
                            >Capoianu–Costa–Nicolae</hi> 2022,
                    1404–1405.</note><?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?></p>
                <p xml:id="p.6">[Aliud]<?oxy_custom_end?><note type="critic" xml:id="note.7"><hi
                            rend="smallcap">Ipolyi</hi> 1875, 587. In Romanian: <hi rend="smallcap"
                            >Albu–Capoianu</hi> 1974, 158; <hi rend="smallcap"
                            >Capoianu–Costa–Nicolae</hi> 2022,
                    1404–1405.</note><?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?></p>
                <p xml:id="p.7">[Aliud]<?oxy_custom_end?><note type="critic" xml:id="note.8"><hi
                            rend="smallcap">Ipolyi</hi> 1875, 587. In Romanian: <hi rend="smallcap"
                            >Albu–Capoianu</hi> 1974, 158; <hi rend="smallcap"
                            >Capoianu–Costa–Nicolae</hi> 2022,
                    1404–1405.</note><?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?></p>
                <p xml:id="p.8">[Aliud]<?oxy_custom_end?><note type="critic" xml:id="note.9"><hi
                            rend="smallcap">Ipolyi</hi> 1875, 587–588. In Romanian: <hi
                            rend="smallcap">Albu–Capoianu</hi> 1974, 158; <hi rend="smallcap"
                            >Capoianu–Costa–Nicolae</hi> 2022,
                    1404–1407.</note><?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?></p>
